"This script's run form comes from its own command-line arguments. "
"Managing a hardcoded constant here would replace that form — leave it as "
"is."
msgstr "这个脚本的运行表单来自它自己的命令行参数。在这里纳管一个写死的常量会取代那张表单——保持原样即可。"

#: src/skit/tui_settings.py:238
msgid "Detected but not yet managed — tick to manage:"
msgstr "检测到但尚未纳管——勾选即纳管："

#: src/skit/tui_settings.py:248
msgid "Every input() is managed — this script can now run with --no-input."
msgstr "所有 input() 都已纳管——这个脚本现在可以用 --no-input 自动化。"

#: src/skit/tui_settings.py:266
msgid "None yet — press Ctrl+S inside the run form to save one."
msgstr "还没有——在运行表单里按 Ctrl+S 就能存一组。"

#: src/skit/tui_settings.py:270
msgid "Untick a preset to delete it on save:"
msgstr "取消勾选的参数组合会在保存时删除："

#: src/skit/tui_settings.py:289
msgid "Python constraint, e.g. \">=3.11\" (empty = automatic)"
msgstr "Python 约束，例如 \">=3.11\"（留空＝自动）"

#: src/skit/tui_settings.py:294
#, python-format
msgid "Script settings · %(name)s"
msgstr "脚本设置 · %(name)s"

#: src/skit/tui_settings.py:326
msgid "Everything still matches the script."
msgstr "所有定义仍与脚本相符。"

#: src/skit/tui_settings.py:354
#, python-format
msgid "Deleted previously remembered value(s): %(names)s"
msgstr "已删除先前记住的值：%(names)s"

#: src/skit/uvman.py:76
#, python-format
msgid ""
"skit needs Astral's uv to run Python scripts, but it wasn't found on this"
" system. Download uv %(version)s into skit's private directory "
"(%(path)s)? This won't touch your PATH or global environment. [Y/n]"
msgstr ""
"skit 需要 Astral uv 才能运行 Python 脚本,但系统上找不到。要下载 uv %(version)s 到 skit "
"的私有目录(%(path)s)吗?不会动到你的 PATH 或全局环境。[Y/n]"

#: src/skit/uvman.py:118
#, python-format
msgid "Unsupported platform: %(platform)s"
msgstr "不支持的平台:%(platform)s"

#: src/skit/uvman.py:199
#, python-format
msgid "No uv binary found inside the archive: %(path)s"
msgstr "压缩包内找不到 uv 可执行文件:%(path)s"

#: src/skit/uvman.py:231
#, python-format
msgid ""
"No pinned checksum for platform %(triple)s; refusing to run an unverified"
" uv."
msgstr "没有为平台 %(triple)s 预置校验和,拒绝运行未经校验的 uv。"

#: src/skit/uvman.py:238
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Downloaded uv failed its checksum (the mirror may be compromised or the "
"file corrupt). Expected %(expected)s, got %(actual)s."
msgstr "下载的 uv 未通过校验(镜像可能被篡改,或文件已损坏)。期望 %(expected)s,实际为 %(actual)s。"

#: src/skit/uvman.py:254
msgid ""
"Download declined. Install uv yourself (https://docs.astral.sh/uv"
"/getting-started/installation/) and skit will pick it up automatically."
msgstr ""
"已取消下载。你可以自行安装 uv(https://docs.astral.sh/uv/getting-"
"started/installation/),skit 会自动检测并使用。"

#: src/skit/uvman.py:261
#, python-format
msgid "First run — downloading uv %(version)s…"
msgstr "首次运行:正在下载 uv %(version)s…"

#: src/skit/uvman.py:282
#, python-format
msgid "Failed to download uv: %(error)s"
msgstr "uv 下载失败:%(error)s"

#: src/skit/uvman.py:286
